<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>TOE.xyz — Token Exchange</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    background: #0a0a0a;
    color: #fff;
}
header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 20px 40px;
    align-items: center;
}
.logo {
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 22px;
}
.hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 100px 20px;
}
.hero h1 {
    font-size: 56px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.hero p {
    color: #aaa;
    font-size: 20px;
}
.cta {
    margin-top: 30px;
}
button {
    background: #00ffcc;
    border: none;
    padding: 15px 30px;
    font-size: 16px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
}
.section {
    padding: 80px 40px;
}
.features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
}
.card {
    background: #111;
    padding: 25px;
    border-radius: 10px;
}
footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px;
    color: #666;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <div class="logo">TOE.xyz</div>
    <nav>
        <a href="#" style="color:white; margin-right:20px;">Products</a>
        <a href="#" style="color:white;">Login</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
    <h1>The Future of Token Exchanges</h1>
    <p>Trade, analyze, and discover digital assets across global markets.</p>
    <div class="cta">
        <button>Launch App</button>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <h2>Platform Features</h2>
    <div class="features">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Aggregated Liquidity</h3>
            <p>Access top exchanges in one unified interface.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Real-Time Data</h3>
            <p>Live token prices, volume, and on-chain metrics.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Smart Routing</h3>
            <p>Automatically get the best execution price.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>AI Insights</h3>
            <p>Predictive analytics for smarter trading decisions.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <h2>Supported Exchanges</h2>
    <p style="color:#aaa;">Binance · Coinbase · Kraken · Uniswap · Bybit · OKX</p>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <h2>Join the Future of Finance</h2>
    <button>Get Early Access</button>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 TOE.xyz — Token Exchange</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
